Tupinamba-33333333,Tupinamba,Opa ko mbo mosapɨr mɨsã ʔara sɨk'eme , apɨaβamo osɨ rɨgé swi Tupã taʔɨra ʔarʔiré , mosapɨr moruβiʃaβa , Reis ʔiaβa , kwarasɨ sembaβa kotɨ swi ourɨβaʔe , jasɨtatá serekoarama resé , Tupã remimoɲanga pɨsasu pe jaramo iʃupé ogueru jetanongaβamo itajuβa , ɨsɨkatã sɨapwanɨβaʔe , mirra , mosanga toʔo swi",,,"Three chiefs, said to be king, who came from the orient through the guardian star that god had made new as indicator of the path, brought him as offering: gold, incense and myhrr, after god's son was born from his mother's womb, when the thirteenth day came  Catálogo January 6",English,,"# sent_id = 33333333

# text = Opa ko mbo mosapɨr mɨsã ʔara sɨk'eme , apɨaβamo osɨ rɨgé swi Tupã taʔɨra ʔarʔiré , mosapɨr moruβiʃaβa , Reis ʔiaβa , kwarasɨ sembaβa kotɨ swi ourɨβaʔe , jasɨtatá serekoarama resé , Tupã remimoɲanga pɨsasu pe jaramo iʃupé ogueru jetanongaβamo itajuβa , ɨsɨkatã sɨapwanɨβaʔe , mirra , mosanga toʔo swi

# text_eng = Three chiefs, said to be king, who came from the orient through the guardian star that god had made new as indicator of the path, brought him as offering: gold, incense and myhrr, after god's son was born from his mother's womb, when the thirteenth day came  Catálogo January 6
